Document: OpenXRCompositionLayerEquirect  
Path: godot/classes/class_openxrcompositionlayerequirect.rst  
Summary: Properties and their descriptions for the OpenXRCompositionLayerEquirect class, including default values, accessors, and usage notes.  

central_horizontal_angle (float): The central horizontal angle of the sphere. Used to set the width. Default: 1.5707964. Accessor methods: set_central_horizontal_angle(value: float), get_central_horizontal_angle() → float.  
fallback_segments (int): The number of segments to use in the fallback mesh. Default: 10. Accessor methods: set_fallback_segments(value: int), get_fallback_segments() → int.  
lower_vertical_angle (float): The lower vertical angle of the sphere. Used together with upper_vertical_angle to set the height. Default: 0.7853982. Accessor methods: set_lower_vertical_angle(value: float), get_lower_vertical_angle() → float.  
radius (float): The radius of the sphere. Default: 1.0. Accessor methods: set_radius(value: float), get_radius() → float.  
upper_vertical_angle (float): The upper vertical angle of the sphere. Used together with lower_vertical_angle to set the height. Default: 0.7853982. Accessor methods: set_upper_vertical_angle(value: float), get_upper_vertical_angle() → float.